---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 170
  - Title: The Testament of Judah
    Location: XX 1-2
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Volition
---
Know, therefore, my children, that two spirits wait upon man -- the
spirit of truth and the spirit of deceit. And in the midst is the
spirit of understanding of the mind, to which it belongeth to turn
whithersoever it will.
